{"tid":1550614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【正視聽】叫人唔好打嘅係藍絲，唔係左膠","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T20:27:56.000Z","uid":40628,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5eac721954d036fa05d415526c8e17221b6a0fd9","tid":1550614,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"有幾次明顯有啲扮自己人嘅人士，一有藍絲被圍就上前叫人唔好打，不論北角，油麻地，荃灣同今日將軍澳都有發生。 <br />\n<br />\n事後亦有手足影到相，叫人唔好打嘅有同藍絲一齊走。正常思考都諗到，藍絲唔會一個人咁勇走入示威人群入面，扮左膠叫人唔好打係佢哋最大保護。<br />\n<br />\n我好肯定話俾你哋聽，嗰啲唔係左膠。因為社運最左膠嘅社工都企係前線擋警察，佢哋見盡手足火魔法水魔法，如果要阻嗰陣已經阻咗，唔會仲幫口係前線同警察理論。<br />\n<br />\ntldr : 1. 唔好屈左膠，2. 有人叫唔好打即拖佢走"},{"pid":"0e1538c2d897142c624ceffee654384d95d94531","tid":1550614,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:50:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea97b56b9105b9fc85ae03360e76c326fd55ceba","tid":1550614,"uid":213379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:53:21.000Z","msg":"兩者同時都會出發就一定係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a52f96e81f30529b6cb3d1a02704a08f1740cec","tid":1550614,"uid":174174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:53:26.000Z","msg":"邊個阻住，咪邊個左膠囉<br />\n無必要洗白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之左膠連埋藍絲一齊打"},{"pid":"43406e1b37f44661fb9a7fbda4b2ecd0bacbaa17","tid":1550614,"uid":40628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8a52f96e81f30529b6cb3d1a02704a08f1740cec","tid":1550614,"uid":174174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:53:26.000Z","msg":"邊個阻住，咪邊個左膠囉<br />\n無必要洗白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之左膠連埋藍絲一齊打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:57:19.000Z","msg":"我哋而家係要認清阻人打係對方策略，亦係藍絲扮嘅和平撚。一定要正視聽嗰啲係藍絲同敵人，手足先唔會中伏。如果下下講左膠又會加深對前線社工嘅誤會"},{"pid":"68233696623c54bec8aba55ce724d0807851f8e5","tid":1550614,"uid":40628,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:00:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠見到手足被捕會後悔，會知自己做錯<br />\n藍絲見到手足被捕會笑啊<br />\n<br />\n識分未啊</span>"},{"pid":"3cadb4a7e9aaf68987a721a2f9978b96410f855b","tid":1550614,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05f17f910814be4d22542f41bc1d53efe5f3726e","tid":1550614,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c38ec39296d6ed17d10b03c1ee117d252be84a2","tid":1550614,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05f17f910814be4d22542f41bc1d53efe5f3726e","tid":1550614,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:03:16.000Z","msg":"thanks"},{"pid":"6e8737feffc8e7902bea4ca27716dfc03dad2962","tid":1550614,"uid":25164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e98a4a53d5ae3e00d7e18278eaf29abbc336b4","tid":1550614,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"隔離po變左屌左膠，唔知詳咩好"},{"pid":"393742f73d0ac1dae4017272c75676ba82cd78ca","tid":1550614,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:34.000Z","msg":"人地而家轉左策略啦<br />\n有d會阻前線走人<br />\n有d會幫自己友走人"},{"pid":"896224e64c45b091f5c9b53b24656bfa9ca8b70b","tid":1550614,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"不要再說「 左膠 」<br />\n<br />\n請說 「 藍絲臥底 」"},{"pid":"b3a9e4342204ee66e05cfb39b4a78c9089fcb8a6","tid":1550614,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:05:45.000Z","msg":"有人叫唔好打就打撚埋,一係鬼一係癲"},{"pid":"7f11f4bc008b3523119fc09840a16de843cf73d8","tid":1550614,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:06:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠永遠都唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑夜 要前線放藍衫走<br />\n結果同一班藍衫轉頭斬斷其他手足手筋腳筋攪到個手足殘廢 同有手足比人爆頭<br />\n到今日岩岩機場 逼手足放個用磚頭爆手足頭既藍絲走<br />\n<br />\n重有依2個月好多單左膠死攬傷人者<br />\n根本班撚樣只係為光環 欺善怕惡<br />\n對住黑社會就淆底唔敢阻黑社會斬人<br />\n對住自己手足 知手足唔會打佢地<br />\n就大大力阻手足還拖 同講廢話訓前線話<br />\n話會扣幾多分 會失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a97dc3e6638335352801ee5c30759c7889c2bb2e","tid":1550614,"uid":1102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:06:09.000Z","msg":"同意，去邊今日自己人冇可能信差佬<br />\n阻住私了一律照打"},{"pid":"c319a167eab5b71a8754196058ceeebfa4be8c4e","tid":1550614,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"